  "page": "Conjectures",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><i><b>Conjectures</b></i> is written by Archmaester <a href=\"/index.php/Timotty\" title=\"Timotty\">Timotty</a>. In the work, Archmaester Timotty suggests that, during King <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon I Targaryen\">Aegon I Targaryen</a>'s <a href=\"/index.php/First_Dornish_War\" title=\"First Dornish War\">First Dornish War</a> (<a href=\"/index.php/4_AC\" title=\"4 AC\">4&#160;AC</a>-<a href=\"/index.php/13_AC\" title=\"13 AC\">13&#160;AC</a>), the <a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\">Targaryens</a> had hoped to turn <a href=\"/index.php/Dorne\" title=\"Dorne\">Dorne</a> against <a href=\"/index.php/House_Martell\" title=\"House Martell\">House Martell</a>, by destroying every castle, keep and holdfast in Dorne, except for the Martell seat of <a href=\"/index.php/Sunspear\" title=\"Sunspear\">Sunspear</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_dorne_against_the_dragons.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_dorne_against_the_dragons.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Conjectures&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiaf_dorne_against_the_dragons.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_dorne_against_the_dragons.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, Dorne Against the Dragons.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260405040833\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.019 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.048 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 115/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8608/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 474/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 148/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 626/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.020/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 4.64 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   43.669      1 -total\n 72.68%   31.737      1 Template:Italic_title\n 13.11%    5.727      2 Template:Date\n 10.50%    4.586      1 Template:Ref\n  7.24%    3.163      1 Template:Ref/core\n  3.04%    1.328      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:20116-0!canonical and timestamp 20260405040833 and revision id 239304\n -->\n",
